{
  "stem": "985.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did get back to Boryslaw in 1993, with my son, which is a year and a half ago.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we got-- with a group of Poles, we got on a train and we went west.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then, subsequently, everybody went somewhere else, and this friend of mine and I, we went to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then there's a whole new life started.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, we met some people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Matter of fact, one-- one girl who had an apartment in-- in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, we abandoned those uniforms and we-- since, when we left Schindler's, each one was given some fabrics that they had in a warehouse.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know, it was like a-- I think a blue fabric and a grey [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we traded in for some-- some old clothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we didn't wear any-- no, not anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, when we-- oh, now I remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We traded in those fabrics in that camp-- in Russian camp-- for some old rags, because we were known already by-- by-- everybody knew us that saw us in those striped uniforms.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we exchanged it there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So then, when we went to reregister again with this group of Poles, we already had quote-unquote 'civilian clothes,' some old rags, and tried to change our appearance.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then th-- this girl had a-- well, apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, like, a one-room or two-room apartment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Krakow, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came-- so they told us-- she happened to-- she was from our town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this friend of mine, we came over there, and there was-- unbelievable picture.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In their living room, bedroom, there were mattresses strung all over, from wall to wall.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she told us that there are, like-- like 10 or 12 people.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
